32	+//!    snapshot of that version through [`StateOps::snapshot`], releasing the
33	+//!    backend lock immediately.
34	+//! 2. **compute** — run the [`ProverOps`] call (including the possibly-slow
35	+//!    `autoprove*` / `apply_method` / `del_*` / `reload` / `load_theory` / edits)
36	+//!    on the snapshot **with no state lock held**. Concurrent requests take their
37	+//!    own snapshots and run in parallel.
