47	+//! so a consumer can supply an asynchronous, internally-caching backend that remains
48	+//! the single owner of theory state. The observed lifecycle (`BEHAVIOR.md` §17) —
49	+//! commit-time monotonic allocation, atomicity under races, retention, in-place
50	+//! mutation, snapshot isolation — is the documented **contract** that backend must
